《'''秘密法藏经'''》，又称《'''秘密经'''》（[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|The Book of Mysteries}} 或 {{lang|en|The Book of Secrets}}；[[希臘語|希臘語]][[羅馬化|轉寫]]：{{transl|el|Ta tōn mustērion}}；[[科普特語|科普特語]]轉寫：{{transl|cop|Pjōme nmmusterion}}；[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]轉寫：{{transl|ar|Sifr al-asrar}}<ref>{{cite book |last=Tardieu |first=Michel |date=2008 |title=''Manichaeism'' |trans-title=摩尼教 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=e9wk7DQRoPoC&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=Pj%C5%8Dme+nmmusterion&source=bl&ots=h9_lhkss5_&sig=csc_jF0v0ZFWMNPM2nwgs-A8fqw&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwilhdC-kuveAhXL34UKHVbLAZwQ6AEwAHoECAAQAQ#v=onepage&q=Pj%C5%8Dme%20nmmusterion&f=false |language=en |location=Champaign, Illinois |publisher=University of Illinois Press |page={{p.|38}} |isbn=9780252032783 |access-date=2018-11-23 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608201703/https://books.google.com/books?id=e9wk7DQRoPoC&pg=PA38&lpg=PA38&dq=Pj%C5%8Dme+nmmusterion&source=bl&ots=h9_lhkss5_&sig=csc_jF0v0ZFWMNPM2nwgs-A8fqw&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwilhdC-kuveAhXL34UKHVbLAZwQ6AEwAHoECAAQAQ#v=onepage&q=Pj%C5%8Dme%20nmmusterion&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>），[[摩尼教|摩尼教]]的[[摩尼七经|七部大经]]之一。这部经书在《[[摩尼光佛教法仪略|仪略]]》中音译为“阿罗瓒部”，音译自中古波斯文「{{transl|pal|razan}}」，意为“'''秘密'''”（{{lang|en|Secrets}}）。<ref>G. Haloun &. W. B. Henning, ''The Compendium of the Doctrines and styles of the Teaching of Mani, the Buddha of Light'', {{p.|207}}.</ref>

== 经名考释 ==

“阿”为翻译成汉语时加的前缀，其本名为“罗瓒”，即[[中古波斯语|中古波斯语]]和[[帕提亚语|帕提亚语]]的razan，意为秘密。

